<h2>Use the fields below to check to see if two words or phrases are anagrams, antigrams or palindromes.</h2>
<form action='/results'>
  <div class='form-group'>
    <label for='word'>Put a word or phrase in here:</label>
    <input type='text' name='word' id='word' class='form-control'>
    <label for='compare'>Put another word or phrase in here:</label>
    <input type='text' name='compare' id='compare' class='form-control'>
  </div>
  <button type='submit' name='Check' class='btn btn-success'>Check</button>
</form>
